						               													<description>Argentina, 1976. The country is submerged in a terminal crisis.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While some fight for a Nation that represents the inclusive, national and popular interests of the great majorities, others operate to make the country an elitist, neo-colonial, surrendering and excluding appendix of the majorities, representing foreign interests and local minorities. In this framework, a collection of perfidious characters sink into lies, pettiness, greed, impunity, fanaticism, betrayal and death, forming part of the complex web of power in Argentine daily life in the 70s.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;OBJECTIVE OF THE GAME&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player must stay alive as he fights to remove the power of his opponents until all influence is wiped out. They will have to know how to hide their secrets very well, be cautious, intelligent, cunning and take care of all the dangers that lurk in each action, infiltrating the ranks of sinister characters to be able to use them until they achieve their goal, die or commit suicide.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Only one (or none) will manage to reach the end of the game, and will try - together with the help of notable personalities - a way out towards the democratic spring of the country.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
